---
import Container from "../Container.astro";
import Button from "../Button.astro";
import { KAKAO, FEATPAPER } from "../../../lib/links";
---

<section class="py-24 sm:py-28">
  <Container>
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-ink px-8 py-16 text-center sm:px-16">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -top-20 size-64 rounded-full bg-primary/30 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-24 -left-10 size-64 rounded-full bg-cyan/20 blur-3xl"></div>
      <h2 class="relative mx-auto max-w-2xl text-balance text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-dark sm:text-4xl">
        AI가 대신 구매하는 시대, 최적화를 마치셨나요?
      </h2>
      <p class="relative mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-on-dark-muted">
        아직 시작하지 않으셨다면, 리드젠랩이 가장 빠른 해결책을 찾아드립니다.
      </p>
      <div class="relative mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <Button href={KAKAO} size="lg">AI 가시성 무료 진단 요청</Button>
        <Button href={FEATPAPER} size="lg" variant="ghost" class="text-on-dark hover:bg-white/10">
          Case Study 보기
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
